Date:   Thu Mar 26 13:25:16 2026 +0900

    Migrate Drive provisioning to admin OAuth; harden tenant isolation; repo hygiene
    
    - backend/routers/admin.py: switch workspace provisioning from service account
      to admin user OAuth (get_user_credentials). Templates live in admin My Drive;
      SA cannot copy them. Stage-by-stage idempotent flow (folder → customer copy →
      work copy → Accounts update → is_active gate). Pre-copy files.get() probe and
      HttpError api_reason surfaced in JSON response. is_active=TRUE only when all
      three keys are confirmed.
    - config.py: correct WORK_REFERENCE_TEMPLATE_ID (wrsZlek→wrsRlek), fix
      PARENT_DRIVE_FOLDER_ID and SHEET_KEY to production values, remove duplicate
      SESS_LOGGED_IN/SESS_USERNAME/DEFAULT_TENANT_ID/SESS_TENANT_ID constants,
      separate ADMIN_CUSTOMER_SHEET_KEY from template IDs.
    - backend/services/tenant_service.py: remove silent ImportError fallback that
      substituted admin sheet key for template IDs. Remove cross-tenant fallback in
      get_customer_sheet_key/get_work_sheet_key — non-default tenants now raise
      ValueError instead of silently reading admin data.
    - core/google_sheets.py: remove first shadowed SA-only get_drive_service().
      Surviving get_drive_service() uses OAuth on both local and server. Guard four
      deprecated provisioning functions with RuntimeError. Update docstring to
      document OAuth-is-required-for-My-Drive rule.
    - .gitignore: add frontend/.next/, offices/, *.gsheet, service_account*.json,
      .claude/, hanwoory/. Narrow broad glob patterns to explicit file names.
    - CLAUDE.md: add project handoff documentation.
    - docs/archive/: move planning/design docs from repo root (not junk — archived).
    - Remove from git index: ~200 build artifacts, desktop.ini, offices/ tenant data,
      test uploads, legacy Streamlit junk, personal notes.
    - Add new source files: backend/routers/manual.py, backend/services/ocr_service.py,
      frontend/app/(main)/manual/page.tsx, frontend/app/(main)/quick-doc/quick-poa/page.tsx.
    
